Package: browser-plugin-freshplayer
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: pepperflashplugin-nonfree
Conflicts: flashplugin-nonfree, flashplayer-mozilla
Description: PPAPI-host NPAPI-plugin adapter
 This package allows one to run the pepper flash plugin (a PPAPI plugin) with
 iceweasel (or any other webbrowser using NPAPI plugins).
